#Method SkImageInfo imageInfo() const

Returns ImageInfo for Canvas. If Canvas is not associated with Raster_Surface or
GPU_Surface, returns SkImageInfo::SkImageInfo() is returned Color_Type is set to kUnknown_SkColorType.



#Example
    SkCanvas canvas;
    SkImageInfo canvasInfo = canvas.imageInfo();
    SkImageInfo emptyInfo;
    SkASSERT(emptyInfo == canvasInfo);
